{"tid":293120,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"假如全香港都被鐵路貫通，技術角度可行嗎？","createTime":"2017-06-22T01:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T09:09:28.000Z","uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b135093bffaaeeb78bc0333d2477916c330facf","tid":293120,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T01:58:36.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/22/094016_0f91155a364f4e555bf32f3e303a4d0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F22%2F094016_0f91155a364f4e555bf32f3e303a4d0b.jpg&h=98e022cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1840000/1840415/20170620_mtr_01_1024.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1840000%2F1840415%2F20170620_mtr_01_1024.JPG&h=e9a4ee96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/VanillaSaint\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FVanillaSaint&d=MMCia7h7ZnaEcZ%2FHRxIRe26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=0a2298b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/VanillaSaint</a><br />\n<br />\n註：當年（2009）嘅香港鐵路最終路線圖作者正是佢本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</div><br />\n<br />\n雲呢嗱聖舵 VanillaSaint 面書專頁最新上載：22 世紀末香港鐵路狂想路綫圖「真實地形版」！雖叫狂想，寫實味濃！作者雲呢嗱聖舵豪言是以「鐵路發展策略 2014」為基礎，以「亂過東京」為目標而製成，科科！地圖是以今天的香港地形為藍本，路綫上共 674 個站幾乎都是真實存在（除了海上機場、世紀城、小蠔城），就像在看香港地圖。<br />\n<br />\n香港鐵路在 22 世紀末被四間鐵路公司瓜分：維多利亞鐵路、沙頭角鐵路、香港鐵路、九廣鐵路；共有 39 條路線，674 個車站；又預測屆時香港將有 1,842 萬人口、交椅洲將成為重要交通樞紐、地底住家變得盛行、有飛行車、以及海上機場，嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n<br />\n年僅 21 歲的神人雲呢嗱聖舵接受了 <a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=MMCia7h7ZnaEcZ%2FHRxIRe26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=9d3ab515\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a> 訪問，讓大家了解更多 22 世紀末香港鐵路狂想路綫圖的創作點滴。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1840415\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1840415&d=MMCia7h7ZnaEcZ%2FHRxIRe26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=66ece6a4\" target=\"_blank\">http://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1840415</a><br />\n<br />\n佢係連登巴打嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div>"},{"pid":"a4f372cab030abe595b0efc17093407d736a4bcc","tid":293120,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T02:05:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=MMCia7h7ZnaEcZ%2FHRxIRe26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=9d3ab515\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a>：花了多少時間製作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n雲呢嗱聖舵：地形版[初版]是去年 8 月製作，花了一星期；然後 12 月以[初版]做底，用了一星期製成現在的[第二版]。（看似很快，其實是由朝到晚，起床就做，做到睡覺，第二日起床繼續）之後偶爾想到改良位，不斷修改，今天誕生 2.3 版。<br />\n<br />\n所以：[初版] 1 星期 +[第二版] 1 星期 +[改良] 零碎幾日 = 3 星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">22 世紀末香港鐵路狂想路綫圖真實地形版：<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0Bw-eR1rLN5HVWU04eW9vYjM1WDA/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F0Bw-eR1rLN5HVWU04eW9vYjM1WDA%2Fview&d=MMCia7h7ZnaEcZ%2FHRxIRe26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=8d15d7d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/0Bw-eR1rLN5HVWU04eW9vYjM1WDA/view</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=MMCia7h7ZnaEcZ%2FHRxIRe26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=9d3ab515\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a>： 一人完成？<br />\n<br />\n雲呢嗱聖舵：對。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=MMCia7h7ZnaEcZ%2FHRxIRe26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=9d3ab515\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a>：用甚麼軟件？<br />\n<br />\n雲呢嗱聖舵：Adobe PhotoShop。不過因為電腦廢，製作地形版（2.3）的時候，因為太多文字太多 layer，所以要拆開 3 個檔案，但都有些 lag。）<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1840000/1840415/20170620_mtr_03_600.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1840000%2F1840415%2F20170620_mtr_03_600.JPG&h=386dbf67&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=MMCia7h7ZnaEcZ%2FHRxIRe26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=9d3ab515\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a>：為何製作這鐵路地圖？<br />\n<br />\n雲呢嗱聖舵：純粹興趣。其實我自小就好喜歡鐵路路綫，常常幻想一些不存在的路綫。於是中三 (2009) 我就用小畫家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 製作了《香港鐵路終極路綫圖》（Google 可以搵到），但當年不懂 PhotoShop。<br />\n<br />\n相隔 7 年 (2016)，我突然想重製一下當年嘅作品。於是我畫好所有基本路綫 + 政府計劃嘅路綫，再重新構思所有幻想的路綫。為何要重新構思？例如中三做的地圖，當中有條綫竟然上到大帽山。當年覺得好玩，今日覺得完全唔 make sense（不合理），所以就刪除。<br />\n<br />\n我是參考香港地圖繪製，只要有人住的地方，我就給它畫條鐵路。目標要像東京鐵路網，有種複雜但深奧的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n有人住就加，非郊野公園的地方優先設站。後期才加上西貢遠郊綫（西貢東）這類旅遊鐵路。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1840000/1840415/20170620_mtr_02_600.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1840000%2F1840415%2F20170620_mtr_02_600.JPG&h=a3c8f308&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"a6d557b786a801f205409bff5e3cc4c2bfd6d84f","tid":293120,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T02:07:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=MMCia7h7ZnaEcZ%2FHRxIRe26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=9d3ab515\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a>：製作地圖的時候，可有從實際可行性及技術層面考慮？<br />\n<br />\n雲呢嗱聖舵：有考慮實際可行性 / 技術層面，但不會想得非常深入，當然因為 title 寫明 22 世紀末，所以我也不會框死自己一定要用「現今技術標準」。換言之，部分路綫可能我會想像成真空管道鐵路，例如離島路綫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=MMCia7h7ZnaEcZ%2FHRxIRe26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=9d3ab515\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a>：為何設定在 22 世紀末，而不是 21 世紀末？<br />\n<br />\n雲呢嗱聖舵：提升狂想空間。因為我不覺得 21 世紀末的香港，會開發這麼多需要鐵路的地方，但22 世紀末就應該有可能。<br />\n<br />\n這幅圖有個盲點在於：你知香港最鍾意填海。而這幅圖其實 9 成路綫都是建基於既有土地，就算有新填海，好多都是基於現有政府計劃。所以 100% 未來的地形甚至鐵路規劃其實會與這幅有出入。<br />\n<br />\n為何我不狂想新填海地？如果我想像得太多「原創填海地」，我怕大家疑惑這個「真係香港」？望住一堆陌生嘅地方，會失去共鳴感。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1840000/1840415/20170620_mtr_05_600.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1840000%2F1840415%2F20170620_mtr_05_600.JPG&h=d7501a87&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=MMCia7h7ZnaEcZ%2FHRxIRe26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=9d3ab515\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a>：不同綫路的列車架數有異，可有想到其實 22 世紀末，可能離島住的人比港島還多？<br />\n<br />\n雲呢嗱聖舵：有，所以除了印洲塘是 3 卡外，其餘離島綫至少都 4 卡。想像今日南港島綫其實得 3 卡的時候&hellip;&hellip; 而且這麼多鐵路綫覆蓋，其實疏導了不少乘客改搭不同路綫，所以列車卡數不用太多。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=MMCia7h7ZnaEcZ%2FHRxIRe26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=9d3ab515\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a>：可有想過，屆時已有飛天車、甚至瞬間轉移，鐵路已無用武之地？<br />\n<br />\n雲呢嗱聖舵：有，地形圖入面已寫了幾項未來設定。不過其實未來是無限可能性，樂觀想就正如你所講，可能的士已經識飛；悲觀想可能香港己經因全球暖化而陸沉，冇人知。所以我不想太多，就以「香港仍然健在，且仍然會用鐵路」的前提去創作。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1840000/1840415/20170620_mtr_04_600.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1840000%2F1840415%2F20170620_mtr_04_600.JPG&h=4cf556e8&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"e360b122940d23397e585a1f6f660cf500ffd3e7","tid":293120,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T03:09:10.000Z","msg":"調景嶺搭去機場要停幾多個站 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db68f473307f38fea091c256dc83ab72bfe32b8","tid":293120,"uid":72831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T03:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e958ab05dfb32165d4411a3106a913d5a27af4c","tid":293120,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T05:38:40.000Z","msg":"FF可以好易, 可行可以好難畫"},{"pid":"b39e52a713cb6ccc9828f351efd6b4e08feb5b2c","tid":293120,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T05:55:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />誇得滯"},{"pid":"4327fd4fa02ca0fff1851483b5d9a7be192a5d50","tid":293120,"uid":70505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T06:20:29.000Z","msg":"你有錢比你做無限工程既實諗到方法咁做,工程公司會好多謝你"},{"pid":"b4b78f1e5586684ae485e2211de9be271805cea1","tid":293120,"uid":49918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T06:23:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c0ac99a50c5aeb356ce057094cd06009e13c1df","tid":293120,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T07:08:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾步路就停一停站，分分鐘搭電車/踩單車仲快過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw我比較想要貫通全港既單車徑/架空單車徑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最難係九龍半島中部, 東鐵綫市區段地下化轉到做單車徑"},{"pid":"ff0132a288e9ef3379efa682a2b9c0d0e7f0d1cc","tid":293120,"uid":648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T07:29:33.000Z","msg":"6百幾個站 六百個地鐵上蓋物業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421c1e65206c392ac19bbbdb27a4152d26b4c9de","tid":293120,"uid":34970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T07:34:43.000Z","msg":"成本太高"},{"pid":"a4cc13ff6ea3e1f57829878f8f5a823391836d97","tid":293120,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T07:38:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成本太高</blockquote><br />\nYou don't say"},{"pid":"20023e95eab389160f927ee57162185fb9b65174","tid":293120,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T08:13:41.000Z","msg":"比錢姐<br />\n無話做唔到"},{"pid":"7c7f4692bcbbf44a397533543c6735863e0a88fe","tid":293120,"uid":123082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T08:53:23.000Z","msg":"應該要學埋日本 分車種 普通 快速 特急 etc<br />\n如果唔係停站都停到你傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23eda5c9b97ed417becaca841c7512433d44a3af","tid":293120,"uid":65071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T08:59:26.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7989dfa3af4d17a73416261c694ad8c577500bb1","tid":293120,"uid":7688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:05:26.000Z","msg":"咁多站無效率<br />\n站站停不如坐巴士"},{"pid":"827489160fac0c0da068572f0bfcaf49d0c1f05e","tid":293120,"uid":118314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:09:28.000Z","msg":"多站呢個問題可以用急行解決 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過咁樣又要起多D路軌，買多D車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}